Special Events & Meetings
A Great Clubhouse and Scenic Views Provide the Perfect Backdrop for Your Event
From casual celebrations to corporate meetings, community events and receptions, Lansbrook Golf Club is the perfect venue to host your next event.
Lansbrook’s friendly and professional staff combined with beautiful surroundings and a casual event space with an inviting outdoor patio which can accommodate events for up to 150 guests make the Lansbrook the perfect choice for your meeting or event.
Lansbrook offers affordable packages and personalized breakfast, lunch and dinner menus for any size budget.
For information on hosting your next event at Lansbrook, please call
(727) 784-7333
.
